---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="获取 Synapse — 5分钟接入指南"
  description="clone一次，3步个性化，打开Claude Code立即拥有44位AI专家团队。完全免费，永久可用。"
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A1628 0%, #0d1f3c 100%); padding: 72px 0 56px;">
    <div class="grid-dots"></div>
    <div class="glow-cyan" style="top:-80px; right:-60px; opacity:0.4;"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <a href="/academy" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-white/40 text-sm hover:text-white/70 transition-colors mb-6">
        <svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 12H5M12 5l-7 7 7 7"/></svg>
        学院首页
      </a>
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-[#FCAD2A] uppercase mb-3">GET SYNAPSE</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4">获取 Synapse</h1>
      <p class="text-white/60 text-lg">clone → 改3个名字 → 打开 Claude Code。5分钟，完全免费。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="glow-line"></div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">

    <!-- Quick start terminal -->
    <div class="mb-14 rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-[var(--color-border)] shadow-md">
      <div class="bg-[#1e1e1e] px-4 py-2.5 flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-[#333]">
        <div class="flex gap-1.5">
          <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#ff5f57]"></div>
          <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#febc2e]"></div>
          <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#28c840]"></div>
        </div>
        <span class="text-[#666] text-xs ml-2">PowerShell — 快速接入（Windows）</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[#0d1117] p-6 font-mono text-sm leading-loose overflow-x-auto">
        <p class="text-[#8b949e] mb-1"># Step 1: clone 仓库到本地</p>
        <p class="text-[#79c0ff]">git clone <span class="text-[#a5d6ff]">https://github.com/lysanderl-glitch/synapse.git</span></p>
        <p class="text-[#79c0ff] mt-1">Rename-Item <span class="text-[#a5d6ff]">synapse</span> <span class="text-[#a5d6ff]">"Claude Code\My-Synapse"</span></p>
        <br/>
        <p class="text-[#8b949e] mb-1"># Step 2: 打开 CLAUDE.md，全局替换（Ctrl+H）</p>
        <p class="text-[#d2a8ff]">Lysander  <span class="text-[#8b949e]">→</span>  <span class="text-[#a8d1a0]">你的CEO名字</span></p>
        <p class="text-[#d2a8ff]">{'{{PRESIDENT_NAME}}'}  <span class="text-[#8b949e]">→</span>  <span class="text-[#a8d1a0]">你的名字</span></p>
        <p class="text-[#d2a8ff]">{'{{COMPANY_NAME}}'}    <span class="text-[#8b949e]">→</span>  <span class="text-[#a8d1a0]">你的公司/团队名</span></p>
        <br/>
        <p class="text-[#8b949e] mb-1"># Step 3: 用 Claude Code 打开文件夹</p>
        <p class="text-[#a8d1a0]">收到问候语 → 体系生效 ✓</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 3 steps detail -->
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-6">详细步骤</h2>

    <div class="space-y-4 mb-14">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="flex gap-5 p-6 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-xl hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow">
        <div class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#FCAD2A]/10 border-2 border-[#FCAD2A] flex items-center justify-center font-extrabold text-[#FCAD2A]">1</div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">Clone GitHub 仓库</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-light)] mb-3">在 PowerShell 中运行，下载到你的 Claude Code 目录：</p>
          <div class="bg-[#0d1117] rounded-lg px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs text-[#79c0ff] overflow-x-auto">
            git clone https://github.com/lysanderl-glitch/synapse.git "$env:USERPROFILE\Claude Code\Synapse"
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-2">💡 文件夹名字随意，后面 Claude Code 打开这个文件夹即可</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="flex gap-5 p-6 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-xl hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow">
        <div class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#028CDC]/10 border-2 border-[#028CDC] flex items-center justify-center font-extrabold text-[#028CDC]">2</div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">个性化配置（2分钟）</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-light)] mb-4">打开 <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-mono">CLAUDE.md</code>，用编辑器全局替换（<strong>Ctrl+H</strong>）：</p>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full text-sm border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
              <thead class="bg-[#F7F8FA]">
                <tr>
                  <th class="text-left px-4 py-2.5 text-[var(--color-text)] font-semibold text-xs">搜索（原值）</th>
                  <th class="text-left px-4 py-2.5 text-[var(--color-text)] font-semibold text-xs">替换为</th>
                  <th class="text-left px-4 py-2.5 text-[var(--color-text)] font-semibold text-xs">说明</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody class="divide-y divide-[var(--color-border)]">
                <tr class="hover:bg-[#F7F8FA]">
                  <td class="px-4 py-2.5 font-mono text-xs text-[#013A7D] bg-[#f0f4ff]">Lysander</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-2.5 text-xs text-[var(--color-text-light)]">你的 AI CEO 名字</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-2.5 text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)]">如 "Alex"、"Aurora"</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="hover:bg-[#F7F8FA]">
                  <td class="px-4 py-2.5 font-mono text-xs text-[#013A7D] bg-[#f0f4ff]">{'{{PRESIDENT_NAME}}'}</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-2.5 text-xs text-[var(--color-text-light)]">你的名字</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-2.5 text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)]">AI 以此称呼你</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="hover:bg-[#F7F8FA]">
                  <td class="px-4 py-2.5 font-mono text-xs text-[#013A7D] bg-[#f0f4ff]">{'{{COMPANY_NAME}}'}</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-2.5 text-xs text-[var(--color-text-light)]">你的公司/团队名</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-2.5 text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)]">出现在组织描述中</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="flex gap-5 p-6 bg-white border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-xl hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow">
        <div class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#013A7D]/10 border-2 border-[#013A7D] flex items-center justify-center font-extrabold text-[#013A7D]">3</div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-2">用 Claude Code 打开，发送任意消息</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-light)] mb-3">打开 Claude Code → <strong>Open Folder</strong> → 选择你的 Synapse 文件夹 → 发送任意内容</p>
          <div class="bg-[#F7F8FA] border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm">
            <p class="text-[var(--color-muted)] text-xs mb-1">预期收到的问候语：</p>
            <p class="text-[#013A7D] font-semibold">"[你的名字]您好，我是 [CEO名称]，Multi-Agents 团队为您服务！"</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-2">⚠️ 如果没有出现问候语：确认 Claude Code 打开的是含 CLAUDE.md 的根目录</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Upgrade section -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#0A1628] to-[#011f5c] rounded-xl p-7 mb-14 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="grid-dots" style="opacity:0.3;"></div>
      <div class="relative z-10">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#FCAD2A]/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
            <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#FCAD2A" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2v4m0 12v4M4.93 4.93l2.83 2.83m8.48 8.48l2.83 2.83M2 12h4m12 0h4M4.93 19.07l2.83-2.83m8.48-8.48l2.83-2.83"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-[#FCAD2A] mb-1">升级体系 — 一句话完成</h3>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-sm mb-3">当 Synapse 发布新版本，直接对你的 AI CEO 说：</p>
            <div class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 rounded-lg px-4 py-2.5 font-mono text-sm text-[#FCAD2A] inline-block">
              "升级 Synapse"
            </div>
            <p class="text-white/50 text-xs mt-3">CEO 自动拉取最新版本 → 运行审计（≥90分）→ 保留你的个人化配置 → 完成</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-6">常见问题</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 mb-14">
      {[
        { q: "数据安全吗？", a: "Synapse 完全运行在你本地，数据不经过任何第三方（除 Anthropic Claude API）。你的对话和文件只在你的设备上。" },
        { q: "需要付费吗？", a: "Synapse 配置包本身完全免费。运行需要 Claude Code 订阅（由 Anthropic 提供，$20/月 Max 计划）。体系本身 $0。" },
        { q: "可以定制团队结构吗？", a: "完全可以。通过编辑 agent-butler/config/organization.yaml 增删团队或Agent，或参考 CUSTOMIZATION_GUIDE.md 深度定制。" },
        { q: "Evolution 版本和 Free 版本有什么区别？", a: "Free 版本是体系快照，一次获取永久可用但不自动更新。Evolution 版本每日/每周同步最新进化成果——新Agent能力、新方法论、升级的执行链。" },
        { q: "支持 Mac/Linux 吗？", a: "支持。Claude Code 跨平台可用，Synapse 体系与操作系统无关。步骤1的 PowerShell 命令可换成 git clone + 普通文件夹操作。" },
      ].map(faq => (
        <details class="group border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-xl">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] text-sm list-none">
            {faq.q}
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[var(--color-muted)] group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-5 pb-4 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-light)]">{faq.a}</div>
        </details>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- Navigation bottom -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-between pt-6 border-t border-[var(--color-border)]">
      <a href="/academy" class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-light)] hover:text-[#028CDC] flex items-center gap-1.5">
        <svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 12H5M12 5l-7 7 7 7"/></svg>
        返回学院首页
      </a>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <a href="/academy/team" class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-light)] hover:text-[#028CDC]">浏览AI团队 →</a>
        <a href="/academy/skills" class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-light)] hover:text-[#028CDC]">查看Skills →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</Layout>
